<talking-about subject="main.c">
	
	<questions>
		<(> Why are update() and render() and on_key(), etc static?
		<((> 
			What does it mean to cast arguments to (void) in update? Why not 
			empty?
			<answer (>
				It means they are intentionally unused to avoid warnings
